  "prompt": "Which is the best college for MBA in Delhi?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" college for an MBA in Delhi can depend on various factors including personal preferences, specialization, career goals, and other considerations. However, some of the most reputed institutions in Delhi known for their MBA programs include:\n\n1. **Indian Institute of Management (IIM) Delhi**: Known for its rigorous academic programs and strong placement records.\n  \n2. **Faculty of Management Studies (FMS), University of Delhi**: Offers a highly regarded MBA program with a focus on academic excellence and a strong ROI.\n\n3. **Indian School of Business (ISB), Mohali (near Delhi)**: Although not in Delhi, it is close and is well-respected for its one-year MBA program aimed at working professionals.\n\n4. **Symbiosis Institute of Business Management (SIBM), Delhi**: Part of the Symbiosis International University, it is known for its diverse curriculum and active placement support.\n\n5. **International Management Institute (IMI), Delhi**: Known for its strong industry connections and good placement statistics.\n\n6. **Institute of Management Technology (IMT), Ghaziabad**: While not in Delhi, it's very close and has a good reputation for its MBA programs.\n\nWhen considering an MBA program, be sure to assess factors such as faculty credentials, course offerings, internship opportunities, and alumni network. Additionally, visiting campuses and speaking with current students can provide valuable insights.",
